inline string query(const map < string , int > & mtp, string u){
    map < string , int > :: const_iterator it;
    long long int mm = -inf;
    string res = "";
    for(it = mtp.begin(); it!=mtp.end(); ++it){
        string tmp = it->first.substr(0,(int)u.size());
        if(tmp==u){
            if(it->second > mm){
               mm = it->second;
               res = it->first;
            }
        }
    }
    return mm > -inf ? res : "NO";
}
